Package edu.ncsu.csc216.ticket_manager.model.ticket

Class Ticket

java.lang.Object
edu.ncsu.csc216.ticket_manager.model.ticket.Ticket
public class Ticket extends Object
Ticket Class Creates the ticket object as well implements the TicketState Interface to hold all six possible ticket states as inner classes
Author:
Max Farthing
